hints.description: This company is a diversified energy company serving customers in Michigan. They operate electric and gas utilities, and also provide energy solutions and technologies. Notably, they are one of the largest investor-owned utilities in the United States and have been investing heavily in renewable energy sources like solar and wind.
hints.funFact1: The company traces its roots back to 1903 when it was formed through the consolidation of several smaller gas and electric companies, initially known as the ***** Light & Power Company.
hints.funFact2: Jerry ****** has served as the CEO since 2010, leading the company through significant growth and a focus on sustainability initiatives.
